	Nonfunctional subdomains:

		- keytool.edev	(shows lmscloud.edev; expired 2013-07-23; mismatched, CN: *.desire2learn.com)


	Fully covered subdomains:

		- (www.)
		- community
		- lmscloud.edev
		- pt.valence


	Observed cookie domains:

		- ^
